#
# Some GIT site and tips to help noobs
#

---------------------------------------------------------------------
http://yannesposito.com/Scratch/fr/blog/2009-11-12-Git-for-n00b/

Récupérer un projet :

git clone ssh://server/path/to/project
Utiliser Git tous les jours :

# get modifications from other
git pull
# read what was done
git log

# Make local changes to files 
hack, hack, hack...
# list the modified files
git status
# show what I've done
git diff

# tell git to version a new file
git add new/file

# commit its own modifications 
# to its local branch
git commit -a -m "Fix bug #321"

# send local modifications to other
git push


